{"tid":177947,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"多維 : 讓中國血流成河ISIS真有這個本事？","createTime":"2017-03-29T08:11:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-29T15:15:40.000Z","uid":30561,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b954e0385ae547a288bd2d7d384a3b0724eb6ad1","tid":177947,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T08:11:34.000Z","msg":"多維 : 讓中國血流成河ISIS真有這個本事？<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.bananadaily.net/images/image/0/25001.jpg?t=1488722735\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bananadaily.net%2Fimages%2Fimage%2F0%2F25001.jpg%3Ft%3D1488722735&h=16be17ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n極端組織&ldquo; 伊斯蘭國 &rdquo;近日發布視頻以&ldquo;血流成河&rdquo;向中國宣戰，然而日本媒體認為，&ldquo;伊斯蘭國&rdquo;在中國策劃和發動大規模襲擊的能力是有限的。<br />\n<br />\n　　日本《外交學者》網站3月4日刊文稱，在&ldquo;伊斯蘭國&rdquo;（ISIS）方面，中國目前為止也經歷了一些挫折。2015年，一名中國公民被ISIS捉為人質，並且被殺害。ISIS主要集中精力應對那些參加打擊它的國際聯盟的國家。中國則因為自己在外交事務中的不干預政策，因而沒有直接參加這場戰鬥。但是中國支持了敘利亞的阿薩德( 專題 )（Bashar al-Assad）政權，而ISIS將之視為一個對手。<br />\n<br />\n　　ISIS本週發布的視頻表明，北京的擔憂慢慢地變成了現實，那就是維吾爾的外國戰士會將ISIS的注意力轉向中國。包括基地組織在內的跨國恐怖集團，在過去基本上不怎麼注意中國，但是ISIS同維吾爾人的融合給中國帶來了特殊的挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n　　文章還說，ISIS走向全球恐怖主義的廣闊前景，以及中國在新疆不斷加劇的鎮壓都確保，中國的領導人會嚴肅對待ISIS本週發布的視頻。正如美國東北大學恐怖主義研究專家艾布拉姆斯(Max Abrahms)2013年所說的，中國在全球不斷擴大的存在使得跨國恐怖主義集團越來越有可能找上門來。<br />\n<br />\n　　<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　　分析認為，ISIS要想在中國發動大規模襲擊不太可能（圖源：AFP/VCG）<br />\n<br />\n　　但是文章最後也指出，ISIS在中國策劃和發動大規模襲擊的能力是有限的。鑑於中國共產黨已經採取非常嚴厲的鎮壓，同時對信息流動實施嚴格控制，包括通過防火牆在全國范圍內實施網絡審查，ISIS慫恿獨狼和隸屬的恐怖集團的常規戰略在中國可能會面臨困難。<br />\n<br />\n　　ISIS最近在網上發布一個近半小時長的視頻，其中有新疆維吾爾武裝分子發誓要返回家鄉，以&ldquo;流血成河&rdquo;向中國宣戰。<br />\n<br />\n　　視頻中的一名維吾爾ISIS成員，在對一名被他稱為是告密者的人進行斬首前，向中國政府發出威脅說，&ldquo;你們這些不明白人民在說什麼的中國人，我們是哈里發(Khalifah ，伊斯蘭教宗教最高統治者之稱號) 的士兵。我們將會找到你們，並以我們的武器當舌頭向你們說明一切，並以流血成河來為那些受壓迫的人復仇。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n　　據澳大利亞國立大學國家安全學院新疆問題專家克拉克（Michael Clarke ）博士的分析，這是外界看到的第一個有關一名講維吾爾語的武裝分子向ISIS效忠的視頻。該視頻顯示，中國現在已成為ISIS聖戰者的攻擊目標。<br />\n<br />\n　　克拉克博士說，視頻說明，迄今為止，ISIS聖戰組織很少在其聲明中提到中國的狀況已發生了重大變化。這似乎也說明，效忠ISIS的維吾爾武裝分子之間可能出現分裂，因為該視頻也對屬於敘利亞基地組織的突厥斯坦伊斯蘭黨（TIP）發出了警告。<br />\n<br />\n　　<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　　中國外交部表示反對一切形式的恐怖主義（圖源：新華社）<br />\n<br />\n　　美國《外交政策》網站3月1日在題為《伊斯蘭國誓言下一個襲擊中國，這就是原因》的文章中稱，乍一看，對於ISIS而言，中國似乎是一個奇怪的目標。中國在中東沒有軍事基地，雖然北京越來越深入地涉及中東地區的能源生意，但是它並沒有參加美國主導的在伊拉克和敘利亞打擊ISIS的聯盟。<br />\n<br />\n　　文章指出，但是專家們認為，中國之所以成為這個恐怖集團的目標，是因為它對待維吾爾人的方式，維吾爾人聚集中國新疆的西部。北京對待那裡的騷亂採取了越來越強硬的措施。<br />\n<br />\n　　美國波莫納學院(Pomona College)研究新疆問題的人類學家杜磊(Dru Gladney)說，中國的反伊斯蘭的政策使得一些溫和的穆斯林走向了極端。華盛頓智庫新美國2016年的一份報告指出，有114名維吾爾人加入了ISIS。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://pic.bkcimg.com/uploads/image/201703/04/1488664003316488.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.bkcimg.com%2Fuploads%2Fimage%2F201703%2F04%2F1488664003316488.jpg&h=5b32799d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://puui.qpic.cn/qqvideo_ori/0/b0359g4j9ss_496_280/0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpuui.qpic.cn%2Fqqvideo_ori%2F0%2Fb0359g4j9ss_496_280%2F0&h=2234936a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://big5.3mt.com.cn/g2b.aspx/idoimg.3mt.com.cn/Article/upload/200808/080803221397158.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbig5.3mt.com.cn%2Fg2b.aspx%2Fidoimg.3mt.com.cn%2FArticle%2Fupload%2F200808%2F080803221397158.jpg&h=01fa7408&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c234882efbee6f1b1599c79cc836465d89a82d7f","tid":177947,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T08:13:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.independent.co.uk/s3fs-public/thumbnails/image/2016/01/22/08/isis.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.independent.co.uk%2Fs3fs-public%2Fthumbnails%2Fimage%2F2016%2F01%2F22%2F08%2Fisis.jpg&h=99b52826&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b162efad561521218a76089659f62ccbdc6fe296","tid":177947,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T08:13:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.corbettreport.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/isis-army-700x430.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.corbettreport.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F09%2Fisis-army-700x430.png&h=ec02a38d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a7bf4355298379e92d989329c4fd82f25688b60e","tid":177947,"uid":39608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T08:20:11.000Z","msg":"ISIS搞支那既死左幾多都係13個<br />\n點流到成條到河都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2e8539610fd191941b8b7ca408edfc98576ad3f","tid":177947,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T08:23:47.000Z","msg":"點似歐洲佬咁hea<br />\n老共呢下威豬啦"},{"pid":"8fdf6d5dcab2b8e282279697bca17564c69e0a7d","tid":177947,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T08:31:04.000Z","msg":"HONGKONG IS NOT CHINA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c66711e596e3e8c4a954084ea8f920d2b68bf21","tid":177947,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T08:32:53.000Z","msg":"又一巴星落&quot;一帶一路&quot;度了"},{"pid":"e85bf261fa337f8a8830e45c8712222531f514cc","tid":177947,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T08:33:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>HONGKONG IS NOT CHINA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係外國人眼中, 邊撚度有分香港同中國<br />\n唔好on9 啦連登仔"},{"pid":"31ece1a2a593f71f529042fd7a6d8e5b8de3f095","tid":177947,"uid":15813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T08:36:25.000Z","msg":"即時諗起恐怖分子係中国比人呃去賣豬仔賣落火坑果篇文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a482494046a101f52aa42baeaddc4c2cf05d5e3","tid":177947,"uid":44646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T08:36:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中國的反伊斯蘭的政策使得一些溫和的穆斯林走向了極端。<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n歐洲對伊斯蘭夠溫和未？"},{"pid":"63ffd1d47e41c66faa9ae73e88bd84aa886268cc","tid":177947,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T08:53:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點似歐洲佬咁hea<br />\n老共呢下威豬啦</blockquote><br />\n香港有飛虎隊未驚過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5222fa478967a2ea4347e71ec11bb2c7b519829f","tid":177947,"uid":66908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T08:55:54.000Z","msg":"中國人人命唔值錢，死咁啲仲多謝你"},{"pid":"424d05c9b97ae9f086125987bde20550c2a21b20","tid":177947,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T09:19:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>HONGKONG IS NOT CHINA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係外國人眼中, 邊撚度有分香港同中國<br />\n唔好on9 啦連登仔</blockquote><br />\n所以咪打句HONGKONG IS NOT CHINA囉on9樓豬 收皮啦"},{"pid":"b5868d494dcb70f44e4218e09a549217f699ddb5","tid":177947,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T09:22:35.000Z","msg":"等睇新俾人解放<br />\n但無人死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19a6dc87cf779deeb2c4de71a744e4fc98ff9dd3","tid":177947,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T09:22:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>等睇新疆俾人解放<br />\n但無人死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"d4d47243a66918e7a0656f9dc66730811375f3ca","tid":177947,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T09:26:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>HONGKONG IS NOT CHINA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係外國人眼中, 邊撚度有分香港同中國<br />\n唔好on9 啦連登仔</blockquote><br />\n所以咪打句HONGKONG IS NOT CHINA囉on9樓豬 收皮啦</blockquote><br />\n好有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff0917639bbc01b0f9cbf1f09fc74b519f310fa5","tid":177947,"uid":55601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T09:27:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即時諗起恐怖分子係中国比人呃去賣豬仔賣落火坑果篇文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nthis?<br />\n阿拉伯半島電視臺對賓拉登的最新採訪。 <br />\n賓.拉登說：中國是全球唯一絕對不能惹的國家！<br />\n原因是這樣的：基地組織曾派出八名恐怖分子襲擊中國。<br />\n結果是：<br />\n一人在炸北京西直門立體交通橋時轉暈在橋上； <br />\n一人在上海坐公車自殺炸彈時擠了兩小時沒擠上車； <br />\n一人在武漢炸超市時，炸彈遙控器被偷； <br />\n一人在炸成都政府大樓時,被保安狂揍：'叫你討薪，叫你上訪'， <br />\n一人成功地河北炸礦，死傷數百人，潛回基地後，半年沒見任何新聞報導，遂被基地組織以'撒謊罪'處決了； <br />\n一人曾經嘗試炸廣州，結果剛一出火車站,炸藥包就給飛車黨搶了，半天沒恍過神； <br />\n一人剛到中國就失聯後來在上海醫院找到，人還在昏迷醫生說他喝到假酒， 但讓他昏迷到現在的是黑心食品； <br />\n最近，派一女恐怖分子去炸河南，結果被騙到海南島賣淫 !<br />\n記得！<br />\n中國是全球唯一絕對不能惹的國家"},{"pid":"f1c82c03485b0bf26a48116af7f8aa454844297a","tid":177947,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T09:53:06.000Z","msg":"賤命太多 有排殺<br />\n相反令到佢地內哄就容易<br />\n參考滿清 老毛治國術"},{"pid":"964c28da59ad87e4aedf086942ae3f70c2bcf9ad","tid":177947,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T09:58:28.000Z","msg":"歷史上每次回族造反都係血流成河"},{"pid":"69335b73ce65bcb8dedc6c2ea422640d7778fd62","tid":177947,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T10:23:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d76b8668d7dff7598bc57fd3b3741cafc8d0af0","tid":177947,"uid":32325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T10:30:49.000Z","msg":"咁又係<br />\n講到殺支那人全世界邊有人夠你哋支那人咁叻吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"396236c35ae1114042de98032c48bc0c56e6b8d0","tid":177947,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T11:40:49.000Z","msg":"如果大家有睇新聞<br />\n<br />\nISIS 家陣係伊拉克和敘利亞 都節節失敗, 比人圍到仆街<br />\n連個領袖 都走左佬, 唔知去左邊...........ISIS 份子又要扮女人走佬<br />\n佢地連自己都理唔掂, 仲邊有時間去搞其他野<br />\n<br />\n估計將來多數都係 維族人發動攻擊, 然後ISIS 又衝出來認功"},{"pid":"a63ab71d96535297a00564213743b0c3a51bb2d4","tid":177947,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T12:06:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>歷史上每次回族造反都係血流成河</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n李自成, 黃巢, 太平天國 仲勁過回族多多聲<br />\n佢地直情食人肉"},{"pid":"1ba61650703030b5c38f8df519424c23378dbd19","tid":177947,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T12:20:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>歷史上每次回族造反都係血流成河</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n李自成, 黃巢, 太平天國 仲勁過回族多多聲<br />\n佢地直情食人肉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實Isis 入侵中國，只會幫助中共提早完成中亞的一帶一路既國策，大多數人認為中國一帶一路只係送錢去中亞係Failed state, 正因為中國共產黨係果個地域度未立腳，重建古代絲綢之路係冇有可能，但isis，比到中國絕佳嘅理由去進軍中亞，未來中國， 走向軍國主義的機率非常高，走向戰爭之路，難以避免。<br />\n<br />\n中國的軍事實力，中亞小國不是中共的對手。面對共產黨的滲透，中亞人民反抗嘅力量係不大，新疆已經係一個例子。相信中國未來會加強增壓維吾爾族， 強迫其反抗，引誘伊斯蘭武裝勢力一舉殲滅。<br />\n<br />\n一帶一路走向成熟只會係時間嘅問題，不久將來中國不再依賴香港。早一點取消香港關係法，反而為令到親中的香港人醒覺，為香港帶來意想不到的效果。"},{"pid":"e8042bdbc2a56ed91006f7cef653ec8309d30951","tid":177947,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:08:16.000Z","msg":"激將法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}